export const styles = {
	customInput: {
		width: '100%',
		height: '50px',
		background: 'rgba(210, 210, 210, 0.25)',
		border: '2px solid #d2d2d2',
		boxSizing: 'border-box',
		borderRadius: '5px',
		padding: '1rem',
		color: 'white',
		fontSize: '1.2rem'
	},
	customInputTitle: {
		width: '100%',
		height: '50px',
		background: 'rgba(210, 210, 210, 0.25)',
		border: '2px solid #d2d2d2',
		boxSizing: 'border-box',
		borderRadius: '5px',
		padding: '1rem',
		color: 'white',
		fontSize: '1.2rem',
		width: '160%'
	},
	customInputFile: {
		width: '100%',
		height: '50px',
		background: 'rgba(210, 210, 210, 0.25)',
		border: '2px solid #d2d2d2',
		boxSizing: 'border-box',
		borderRadius: '5px',
		padding: '1rem',
		color: 'white',
		fontSize: '1.2rem',
		width: '40%',
		justifySelf: 'right',
		display: 'none'
	},

	satuLine: {
		display: 'grid',
		gridTemplateColumns: 'repeat(2, 1fr)'
	}
};
